OL,7,FShe and her 11-year-old son Rex are
OL,8,Fforced to share a bed and the flat is
OL,9,Falso ridden with rats.
OL,11,FOsa tell ITV London: "It's very
OL,12,Fheartbreaking. It's very terrible.
OL,14,F"It's not a good situation, especially
OL,15,Ffor my son.
OL,17,F"He's 11 years old, not taking a
OL,18,Fshower before going to school."
