OL,7,FThe conditions are having such an
OL,8,Fimpact on Rex, who is just 11-years-
OL,9,Fold, that his school has written to
OL,10,Fthe council for help.
OL,12,FToday, Rex told us his living
OL,13,Fsituation causes him "stress and
OL,14,Ftrauma".
OL,16,FHe told ITV London, "I feel bad about
OL,17,Fmyself having to sit next to someone
OL,18,Fknowing that I smell very bad. "
