OL,7,FThere is a communal bathroom shared
OL,8,Fwith other residents in the building,
OL,9,Fbut it's often out of order.
OL,11,FOsa says she's complained to Lambeth
OL,12,FCouncil but, "they don't care".
OL,14,FThey should have been for a maximum of
OL,15,F56 days but they have been in the
OL,16,Ftemporary accommodation for more than
OL,17,Fa year and a half.
OL,19,F"No one has ever come here with all
OL,20,Fthe complaints and emails that I have
OL,21,Fsent," she says.
