OL,7,FLambeth Council apologised and said it
OL,8,Fhas carried out work on the flat,
OL,9,F"including remedial work in removing
OL,10,Fair locks and changing water flow."
OL,12,FA council spokesperson told ITV London
OL,13,Fsaid: "We have checked the supply this
OL,14,Fmorning and confirmed that all cold-
OL,15,Fwater outlets are working, so the
OL,16,Fproperty has a working toilet.
OL,18,F"Hot water is available throughout the
OL,19,Fbuilding, although the pressure varies
OL,20,Fon different floors.
